title: Dum Man Of Power
subTitle: Tarak comes to India after his parents die in an accident and falls in love with Meera, who seeks others' happiness before hers. Soon, Tarak and Meera's relationship goes through a rough patch.

title: Action Blaster

title: Seetharama Kalyana
subTitle: Arya, a righteous man, falls in love with a small-town woman named Geetha, unaware of the obstacles that lie ahead for both of them.

title: Roberrt
subTitle: Raghava, the head cook in a catering unit, leads a peaceful life with his son Arjun. However, their bliss is short-lived as Raghava's past comes back to haunt him.

title: Dashing CM Bharath
subTitle: Oxford graduate Bharat assumes his late father's role as chief minister. He strives to reform a corrupt society, but encounters fierce opposition from adversaries.

title: Geetanjali 2

title: Naa Saami Ranga

title: Gambler No. 1
subTitle: Janaki agrees to marry her childhood friend Rummy, but not until he's become rich and powerful, so Rummy decides to become a gambler.

title: Alluri
subTitle: Iqbal, an aspiring police candidate, embarks on a journey to follow in the footsteps of Alluri, an upright officer, and discovers valuable lessons along the way.

title: Surya's Saturday
subTitle: A vigilante fights against injustice using his own unique moral code, where he only comes out to play on Saturdays.

title: The Return Of Lion
subTitle: When a social worker dies, his son must not only avenge his death but also prove his innocence when the welfare fund money accumulated by his family goes missing.
